                googleMaps: 'https://goo.gl/maps/1dZ1JD64e8umZ7n18',
                aboutHr:
                    'Planinarski dom "Blidinje" nalazi se uz obalu Blidinjskog jezera između planinskih masiva Vrana (2074 m) i Čvrsnice (2228 m) u Parku prirode Blidinje na nadmorskoj visini od 1190 m.<br> Vrijednim radom planinara nekadašnja stara šumarska kuća, koju je Općina Tomislavgrad dala Društvu na upravljanje, izrasla je u planinarski dom koji se danas može pohvaliti zavidnom infrastrukturom.<br><br> Pored 36 udobnih ležaja kojima raspolaže, dom ima osiguranu električnu energiju, vodu, grijanje, sanitarni čvor s tuševima, kao i kuhinju ponuđenu planinarima za samostalno pripremanje obroka. U prostranom dnevnom boravku imate mogućnost opustiti se uz pucketanje vatre iz kamina, gledanje utakmica, a zahvaljujući Wi-Fi mreži možete podijeliti fotografije s prijateljima. U pomoćnom objektu posjetitelji imaju mogućnost pripreme roštilja u velikom kaminu, mogu boraviti u lijepo uređenom dvorištu i zaigrati buća ili jednostavno sjediti i uživati u pogledu na naš planinski biser - Blidinjsko jezero i krševitu Čvrsnicu.<br><br>Dom je prikladan i za momačke ili djevojačke zabave kao i sve druge oblike druženja.<br><br>Za ugodan boravak brine se ljubazni domar Toma, a za više informacija možete nas kontaktirati na mail orlovastina1999@gmail.com ili na brojeve telefona +387 63 812 089, +387 63 330 420.<br><br>Dragi gosti, želimo vam ugodan boravak u našem domu!',
                aboutEn:
                    "The mountain lodge 'Blidinje' is located on the shore of Lake Blidinje between the mountain massifs of Vran (2074 m) and Čvrsnica (2228 m) in the Blidinje Nature Park at an altitude of 1190 m.<br> Thanks to the hard work of mountaineers, the former old forest house, that the Municipality of Tomislavgrad gave to the Society on management, has grown into a mountain lodge that today boasts an enviable infrastructure.<br><br>In addition to the 36 comfortable beds available, the lodge has electricity, water, heating, sanitary facilities with showers, as well as a kitchen offered to mountaineers to prepare their own meals. In the spacious living room, you can relax with the fire crackling from the fireplace, watch sports, and thanks to the Wi-Fi network, you can share photos with your friends. In the auxiliary facility, visitors have the option of preparing a barbecue in the large fireplace, they can stay in the beautifully decorated yard and play bocce or simply sit and enjoy the view of our mountain pearl - Lake Blidinje and the craggy Čvrsnica.<br><br>The home is also suitable for bachelor or bachelorette parties as well as all other forms of socializing.<br><br>The friendly caretaker Toma takes care of your pleasant stay, and for more information you can contact us at the email orlovastina1999@gmail.com or at the phone numbers +387 63 812 089, +387 63 330 420.<br><br>Dear guests, we wish you a pleasant stay in our home!",
